# Project Configuration

## Language
language: cpp
standard: c++17
compiler: clang++

## Build System
build_system: cmake
cmake_minimum: 3.20
package_manager: conan2

## Project Structure
layout: pitchfork
source_extension: .cc
header_extension: .h
test_extension: _test.cc

## Documentation
documentation: doxygen
documentation_style: brief
documentation_coverage: public_api

## Testing
test_framework: catch2
test_style: bdd
coverage_tracking: true

## Static Analysis
static_analysis:
  - clang-tidy
  - clangd
  - sanitizers

## Compiler Flags
compiler_flags:
  - -Wall
  - -Wextra
  - -Werror 